         <div>
            <head>“I TOO”</head>
            <lg>
               <l enjamb="no">I, too, sing America.</l>
            </lg>
            <lg>
               <l enjamb="no">I am the darker brother.</l>
               <l enjamb="yes">They send me to eat in the kitchen</l>
               <l enjamb="no">When company comes.</l>
               <l enjamb="no">But I laugh,</l>
               <l enjamb="no">And eat well,</l>
               <l enjamb="no">And grow strong.</l>
            </lg>
            <lg>
               <l enjamb="yes">To-morrow</l>
               <l enjamb="yes">I’ll sit at the table</l>
               <l enjamb="yes">When company comes</l>
               <l enjamb="yes">Nobody ’ll dare</l>
               <l enjamb="no">Say to me,</l>
               <l enjamb="yes">“Eat in the kitchen”</l>
               <l enjamb="no">Then.</l>
            </lg>
            <lg>
               <l enjamb="yes">Besides, they’ll see how beautiful I am</l>
               <l enjamb="no">And be ashamed,—</l>
            </lg>
            <lg>
               <l enjamb="no">I, too, am America.</l>
            </lg>
            <byline>Langston Hughes</byline>
         </div>
      </body>
